title: Olive Express
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan suitable dishes include house-made falafel, hummus, baba ganoush, salads, portobello panini, chickpea panini, mixed vegetable platter (roasted eggplant, chickpeas and mixed vegetables served with rice).
